{"word":"Ahijah","slug":"ahijah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ahijah</b> <a href=\"#/H281\">H281</a> <br/> Called also Ahiah.<br/> 1. Son of Bela<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=8&verse=7'>1Ch 8:7</a><br/> 2. Son of Jerahmeel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=25'>1Ch 2:25</a><br/> 3. A priest in Shiloh<br/> - Probably identical with Ahimelech<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=22&verse=11'>1Sa 22:11</a> <br/> - Was priest in Saul's reign<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=14&verse=3'>1Sa 14:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=14&verse=18'>1Sa 14:18</a> <br/> - Slain<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=22&verse=19'>1Sa 22:19</a> <br/> 4. One of David's heroes, called Eliam<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=11&verse=36'>1Ch 11:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=23&verse=34'>2Sa 23:34</a><br/> 5. A Levite who was treasurer in the tabernacle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=26&verse=20'>1Ch 26:20</a><br/> 6. Son of Shisha<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=3'>1Ki 4:3</a><br/> 7. A prophet in Shiloh<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=11&verse=39'>1Ki 11:39</a><br/> 8. Father of Baasha<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=15&verse=27'>1Ki 15:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=15&verse=33'>1Ki 15:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=9&verse=9'>2Ki 9:9</a><br/> 9. An Israelite, who subscribed to the covenant of Nehemiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=26'>Neh 10:26</a>"}]}